    <div class="app_body">
      <br>
        <blockquote>
          <h3 id="intro">Here's an app that demonstrates my infinite knowledge of Backbone.js! You can use the form below to tweet to yourself (hints the name). Every tweet can be deleted, updated and liked in the feed below. How exciting!</h3>
        </blockquote>
        <br>
        <div class="jumbotron">
          <div class="profile_info">
          <img src="/images/taco.gif" id="profile_pic">
